---
title: Portuguese-Style Prawns & Tomato Rice with Lemon & Parsley
description: Take your taste buds on a trip to Portugal with these succulent prawns! Served over a rich, tomato-infused rice and finished with
a sprinkle of parsley, this dish is a perfect balance of warmth, zest and indulgence. Dig in!
